{"tid":441658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女出軌比率較港男高","createTime":"2017-10-20T00:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T03:13:02.000Z","uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"285077c2dcae990f1c5cd05f8c500f54da7604e4","tid":441658,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"港女出軌比率較港男高　雖偷食但我還愛你<br />\n<br />\n有人說男人愛出軌，但一項調查發現，港女自認曾出軌比率較港男高，百分比亦大幅拋離新加坡、馬來西亞及泰國等地。<span style=\"color: red;\">該個由約會平台進行的調查訪問了330名港男港女，當中24%受訪女士承認曾出軌，男士則有18%。</span>綜合男與女，有20%受訪者自覺未來有出軌機會，近半數人更認為出軌不等於不愛現任，細水長流愛情觀已變成：「無事嘅！偷食，但還愛你。」<br />\n<br />\n兩性相處之道非常微妙，甚麼才算出軌？「逢場作興」又算不算？男女看法大不同。該項調查顯示，有48%受訪者曾經被背叛，近70%受訪男女認為出軌是包括心靈與身體的背叛，但相對來說，<span style=\"color: red;\">男士對出軌標準看得嚴謹一些，有26%人認為身體上的背叛、即使「我同佢無感情」已算出軌，反而只有約20%女士認為身體上背叛是出軌。</span><br />\n<br />\n結果又顯示，43%受訪者推翻「出軌等於不愛伴侶」說法，<span style=\"color: red;\">有52%港女認為出軌皆因好奇心重</span>，亦有37%受訪者表示如果有更吸引的對象出現，不論對方與自己是否單身都會嘗試發展。負責該項調查的esync行政總裁兼兩性關係專家Violet Lim指，很多人因好奇心而開展一段關係，以為吸引對方後大家很自然會走下去，但其實有相近價值觀及懂得尊重對方才是長遠發展的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=7ZPDSQTsmiNi9oVSPo2u3zM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=66dc32a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>"},{"pid":"21762f59daf421c937b8475ae1e574faa1db6cc7","tid":441658,"uid":97119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"f94732124bec708f45f6e9f7704ff1f28c244aa2","tid":441658,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98581a4870e71046c55c7e7446b3ccd100a69585","tid":441658,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"得香港做雞可以做到咁高調同咁貴"}]}